title: Jessica lifts expectations for Commonwealth Games berth (The University of Notre Dame Australia)
text: ( Source : The University of Notre Dame Australia ) Physiotherapy student and Elite Athlete , Jessica Lai, will represent Australia at the 2015 International Weightlifting Federation ( IWF ) World Championships in Houston, USA , on 20 November . 21
